                            <h4>10 Mobile App Development Trends need to be adopted</h4>
                            <h4><strong>1. Chatbot Integration in Existing Mobile App</strong></h4>
                            <p>“Chatbots market is growing at a CAGR of 37.11% and it is expected to reach USD 6 Billion by the end of 2023.”</p>
                            <p>The above statistic proves that the Chatbots market is growing with immense speed. To give a stimulating user experience, business apps should be combined with Chatbots, hence providing better customer interaction.</p>
