                            <p>A number of businesses have promoted Chatbot development and had got integrated it with their mobile apps while you are just thinking to get the one!</p>
                            <h4><strong>2. Artificial Intelligence in Mobile App Development Market</strong></h4>
                            <p>Voice-enabled technology has brought a revolution in the artificial intelligence industry. After releasing Google Assistant and Siri, it has become mandatory for iOS/Android developers to embrace AI in their mobile app development process to give a better experience and enhance mobile app capabilities. Businesses can engage efficiently with their customers by using mobile tools which can access real-time insights through machine learning technologies, advanced analytics, and cognitive interfaces.</p>
                            <h4><strong>3. Augmented Reality and Virtual Reality </strong></h4>
                            <p>Perceptible that AR and VR are being used more in the entertainment industry but the time is no far when these technologies will dominate other industries too. AR and VR mobile apps give a real-life environment and recreate real-life situations. Big industries are increasing their investment in AR and VR projects in order to increase enterprise application development for various industries like healthcare, real estate, retail, manufacturing, food and beverages, and many more.</p>
                            <h4><strong>4. Machine Learning and Recommendation Engines</strong></h4>
                            <p>Your business app should stand out in the crowd by recommending users services or products which best suit them. Latest Android and iOS version beautifully leverages machine learning by implementing recommendation engines into mobile apps. Machine learning algorithms utilize big data collected from different resources, recognize complex patterns and extract useful insights.</p>
                            <h4><strong>5. Enhancing Security with Blockchain Technology</strong></h4>
                            <p>Within a short span of time, blockchain technology has gained huge popularity as of being an infrastructure behind Bitcoins. Not just cryptocurrency will get benefited through blockchain technology but financial ledger apps will be developed for the finance industry. The main goal of using blockchain is to enhance security and incorruptible digital ledgers. These ledgers are shared and highly secured that list out a variety of financial transactions and record transaction history.</p>
                            <h4><strong>6. On-Demand Service Delivery System</strong></h4>
                            <p>On-demand mobile apps have become an integral part of human life by gaining huge popularity in a very short span of time. Users avail themselves of a variety of services like food delivery, taxi, laundry, cleaning, and beauty through an on-demand service delivery system. By delivering on-demand services to customers businesses have boosted revenue by 30% earlier.</p>
                            <h4><strong>7. Memory Inhibition Using Cloud Technologies</strong></h4>
                            <p>Mobile app development trends also include cloud-based app development technology. Enterprises use cloud technologies to develop their business app in accordance to provide smooth operation processes and enhanced productivity. The mobile apps that are built on cloud technologies fetch data from cloud storage which results in a reduction of load on the internal memory. This proves beneficial to business owners as it provides a better user experience.</p>
                            <h4><strong>8. Accelerated Mobile Pages (AMP)</strong></h4>
                            <p>Your audience doesn’t like to wait for more to get the webpage loaded. After Google launched the AMP Project, the online businesses and brand websites have got huge benefits in terms of providing fast webpage loading facilities to users. Accelerated Mobile Pages(AMP) Development regardlessly increases visitors, accelerates content replacement, facilitates mobile search, and enhances ad visibility. AMP adds to a better user experience of web-based cross-platform mobile apps.</p>
                            <h4><strong>9. IoT and Wearables </strong></h4>
                            <p>IoT and wearables are changing the way enterprise mobile apps are developed. Wearables in present days have no feature to get apps installed directly but they can interact with other devices in one or the other way. Custom wearable app development can be done for businesses to make user life easier than ever.</p>
