                                <li aria-level="1">Beacon App Development</li>
                            </ul>
                            <h4><strong>10. Increasing Digital Payments</strong></h4>
                            <p>“Digital Country” is the goal of any country where cashless transaction becomes evident. There are many companies that have implemented digital payment systems for their business transactions. To sustain the goal of a cashless society huge number of businesses have integrated digital wallet facilities for transactions to get done between B2B, B2C, and C2C. Ultimately, digital payment features can benefit companies to harvest data and deliver in-depth analysis about a user.</p>
                            <h4>Conclusion</h4>
